00:39:21.780 --> 00:39:25.890
Then we have h of minus 1, z.

00:39:25.890 --> 00:39:30.790
Then we have h of 0, z
to the 0, which is 1.

00:39:30.790 --> 00:39:36.060
Then we have h of
