00:39:36.060 --> 00:39:40.840
Then we have h of 2, z to
the minus 2, et cetera.

00:39:40.840 --> 00:39:41.340
Right?

00:39:41.340 --> 00:39:44.160
That's what the Z-transform
always looks like.

00:39:44.160 --> 00:39:49.160
