00:40:19.227 --> 00:40:21.560
DENNIS FREEMAN: So they get
increasingly convergent as I

00:40:21.560 --> 00:40:24.360
go to the right.

00:40:24.360 --> 00:40:27.600
If I have z with
a big magnitude,

00:40:27.600 --> 00:40:30.420
